org.liquidplayer.webkit.javascriptcore

Class JSException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • org.liquidplayer.webkit.javascriptcore.JSException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class JSException
extends java.lang.Throwable
    A JSException is thrown for a number of different reasons, mostly by the JavaScriptCore library. The description of the exception is given in the message.
